Package: mobspain
Title: Spanish Mobility Data Analysis Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Prince", "Oppong Boakye", email = "prynx44@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Prince Oppong Boakye [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Prince Oppong Boakye <prynx44@gmail.com>
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for analyzing Spanish mobility patterns using 
    MITMA (Ministry of Transport, Mobility and Urban Agenda) data. Provides 21+ 
    functions for data retrieval, advanced analytics, validation, and visualization. 
    Features include containment analysis, anomaly detection with weekday/weekend 
    context, distance-decay modeling, interactive flow maps, comprehensive 
    mobility indicators, and district-specific analysis with heatmaps and flow 
    visualization. Built on spanishoddata with enhanced performance, 
    intelligent caching, and production-ready data quality tools.
